---
title: Creamy Turkey Pot Pie Pasta with Corn
description: Traditional chicken pot pie is a labour of love—this comfort food favourite is usually an all-day affair. Luckily, we have a time-saving secret. We're transforming it into a pasta dinner.  All the same great flavours in half the amount of time!
